high_descs: Move to the black table to the left of the white table
Pick up the knife on top of the black table with the yellow handle
Slice the apple on top of the black table
Carry the knife to the black table
Place the knife blade side down on the black table in front of the bowl
Move to the black table facing the apple
Pick up an apple slice from the top of the table
Carry the apple slice to the microwave above the oven
Place the apple inside of the microwave, turn on the microwave, remove apple and shut the microwave
Carry the apple to the black table
Place the apple on the front right corner of the black table
anns.task_desc: Heat an apple slice to place on table

high_descs: Turn around and go across the room to the black rack in the corner on your right.
Pick up the knife from the rack.
Cut the apple into thirds.
Move over a few inches to the right.
Set the knife down on the rack between the apple and the bowl with the blade pointing towards you.
Move over a few inches to the left.
Pick up a third of the apple.
Turn right and move across the room to the microwave on your right.
Cook the apple in the microwave for a few seconds and take it back out.
Turn around and go across the room to the black rack on your right.
Set the apple piece down on the rack to the right of the knife blade.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple on the black rack with the knife.

high_descs: turn around and go to the wall and turn to the right and step to the black small table
pick up the knife from the table
slice the apple in three pieces with the knife
turn to the right twice and take a step and turn to the left and take a step and turn to the left
put the knife on the small table
turn to the left and take a step and turn to the right and take a step
pick up one the three pieces of the apple off the table
turn to the right twice and take a few steps to the front of the door and turn to the left and go to the microwave oven
put the piece of apple in the microwave and cook it and when finished it take it out of the microwave
turn to the left twice and go to the door and turn to the right and go to the table
put the slice of apple on the small black table right of the knife
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple on a table
